### Colors

#### Dark Mode (default)
```css
:root {
  /* Backgrounds */
  --bg-primary: #0b0b12;
  --bg-secondary: #13131f;
  --bg-elevated: #1c1c2e;
  --bg-overlay: rgba(11, 11, 18, 0.8);

