## Components

### Layout

#### [NEW] Sidebar.tsx
**Purpose**: Fixed left sidebar with navigation links, logo, and collapse toggle.  
**Props**: None (reads route from `usePathname`)  
**State**: `collapsed: boolean` (persisted to localStorage)  
**Animations**: Width animates between 240px (expanded) and 72px (collapsed) via Framer Motion `animate`. Nav labels fade out when collapsed.  
**Styling**: `bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]`, `border-r border-[var(--border-color)]`, full viewport height. Active link has `bg-[var(--accent-primary)]/10` + `text-[var(--accent-primary)]` + left 3px accent bar.  
**Children**: Logo, 4 nav links (Dashboard, Workouts, Progress, Settings), collapse button at bottom.  
**Interactions**: Hover on links shows background. Click navigates via Next.js `Link`. Collapse button rotates chevron icon.  
**Accessibility**: `<nav>` landmark, `aria-current="page"` on active link.  
**Edge cases**: On mobile (<768px), sidebar is hidden — MobileNav shown instead.

#### [NEW] TopBar.tsx
**Purpose**: Horizontal top bar with page title, search input, notification bell, profile avatar.  
**Props**: `title: string` (current page name)  
**State**: None  
**Animations**: None (static bar)  
**Styling**: `h-16`, `glass` background, `border-b`, sticky top.  
**Interactions**: Search input is visual-only (no functionality). Notification bell has a red dot badge (hardcoded count).

#### [NEW] MobileNav.tsx
**Purpose**: Bottom tab bar visible only on mobile (<768px).  
**Props**: None  
**Styling**: Fixed bottom, 4 equal tabs, `glass` background, `border-t`. Active tab has accent color icon.  
**Interactions**: Tap navigates. Active tab icon scales slightly.

### UI Primitives

#### [NEW] Card.tsx
**Purpose**: Reusable card container with subtle hover glow effect.  
**Props**: `children: ReactNode`, `className?: string`, `hoverable?: boolean` (default true)  
**Animations**: On hover: `y: -3`, subtle glow border appears (via `box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--glow)`). Transition: 300ms ease.  
**Styling**: `rounded-2xl`, `bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]`, `border border-[var(--border-color)]`, `p-6`.

#### [NEW] ProgressRing.tsx
**Purpose**: Circular SVG progress ring for displaying completion percentage.  
**Props**: `value: number` (0-100), `size?: number` (default 120), `strokeWidth?: number` (default 8), `color?: string` (default accent-primary)  
**Animations**: On mount or when `value` changes, the stroke-dashoffset animates from 0% to target via Framer Motion `animate`. Duration: 1s, ease: smooth.  
**Styling**: SVG with background circle (`var(--border-color)`) and foreground circle (gradient or solid color). Center text shows `{value}%`.

### Dashboard Components

#### [NEW] StatCard.tsx
**Purpose**: Displays a single metric (e.g., "Calories Burned: 2,340").  
**Props**: `label: string`, `value: string`, `change?: string`, `changeType?: 'positive' | 'negative' | 'neutral'`, `icon: ReactNode`  
**Animations**: Scroll-triggered fade-up (via AnimatedSection wrapper). Number value counts up on first view (Framer Motion `useMotionValue` + `useTransform` + `animate`). Duration: 1.5s.  
**Styling**: Card with icon top-left (40x40 rounded-xl, accent bg with 10% opacity), value large bold, label caption-size muted, change indicator bottom-right with arrow + color.

#### [NEW] ActivityChart.tsx
**Purpose**: Bar chart showing daily activity for the current week (Mon–Sun).  
**Props**: None (reads from mockData)  
**Animations**: Bars grow from bottom on scroll entry. Stagger: 80ms per bar.  
**Styling**: Card wrapper. Recharts `BarChart` with custom bar shape (rounded top), accent-primary fill, grid lines at 20% opacity. Tooltip on hover.  
**Responsive**: Full width, height 250px on desktop, 200px on mobile.

