## Pages

### / (Dashboard Home)
**Route**: `/`  
**SEO**: `title: "FitPulse — Dashboard"`, `description: "Track your fitness journey with FitPulse"`  
**Layout**:
- Sidebar (left, desktop only)
- TopBar (title: "Dashboard")
- Content area:
  - Row 1: 4 StatCards (Calories, Steps, Active Minutes, Workouts This Week)
  - Row 2: ActivityChart (2/3 width) + CalorieRing (1/3 width)
  - Row 3: RecentWorkouts (2/3 width) + WeeklyGoal (1/3 width)
- MobileNav (bottom, mobile only)

**Responsive**:
- Desktop: Sidebar 240px + content fluid
- Tablet: Sidebar collapsed (72px) + content fluid
- Mobile: No sidebar, full width, MobileNav at bottom. Stat cards 2-column grid. Charts stack vertically.

**Scroll behavior**: Smooth scroll. Each row reveals with staggered AnimatedSection (delay 0, 0.1, 0.2).

### /workouts
**Route**: `/workouts`  
**SEO**: `title: "FitPulse — Workouts"`, `description: "View your workout history"`  
**Layout**:
- TopBar (title: "Workouts")
- WorkoutFilters (pill buttons: All, Strength, Cardio, Flexibility, HIIT)
- Grid of WorkoutCards (2 columns desktop, 1 column mobile)
- 8 workout entries from mock data

### /progress
**Route**: `/progress`  
**SEO**: `title: "FitPulse — Progress"`, `description: "Track your fitness progress"`  
**Layout**:
- TopBar (title: "Progress")
- WeightChart (full width line chart, 6 months of data)
- Row: BodyMetrics (3 cards: Weight, Body Fat %, Muscle Mass)
- PRTable (personal records table: Exercise, Weight, Date)

### /settings
**Route**: `/settings`  
**SEO**: `title: "FitPulse — Settings"`  
**Layout**:
- TopBar (title: "Settings")
- Profile card (avatar, name, email — all mock)
- Preferences card (ThemeToggle, unit system toggle kg/lbs)
- About card (version, links)

