## Animation System

| Element | Technique | Trigger | Duration | Easing |
|---------|-----------|---------|----------|--------|
| Background orbs | CSS `@keyframes float` | Always | 20s loop | ease-in-out |
| Grid pattern | CSS static | Always | N/A | N/A |
| Section reveals | Framer Motion `useInView` | Scroll (once) | 600ms | `--ease-smooth` |
| Stat card numbers | Framer Motion `animate` | In view (once) | 1500ms | `--ease-smooth` |
| Chart bars | Framer Motion stagger | In view (once) | 400ms each, 80ms stagger | `--ease-smooth` |
| Progress ring | Framer Motion `animate` | In view (once) | 1000ms | `--ease-smooth` |
| Card hover | CSS `transition` | Mouse hover | 200ms | ease |
| Button hover | Framer Motion `whileHover` | Mouse hover | Spring (snappy) | spring |
| Sidebar collapse | Framer Motion `animate` | Click toggle | 300ms | `--ease-smooth` |
| Theme transition | CSS `transition` on body | Toggle click | 400ms | ease |
| Page title | Framer Motion fade-in | Route change | 300ms | `--ease-smooth` |

**Performance rules**:
- Background orbs: CSS `@keyframes` only — GPU composited via `transform` + `opacity`, zero JS
- Chart animations: Trigger once with `useInView({ once: true })` — never re-animate on scroll back
- Hover effects: Pure CSS `transition` where possible — Framer Motion only for spring physics
- Never animate `width`, `height`, `top`, `left` — only `transform` and `opacity`

