npm run build    # Expect: 0 errors, all routes statically generated
npm run lint     # Expect: 0 warnings
```

### Visual Checks
- [ ] Dashboard loads with stat card number count-up animation
- [ ] Activity chart bars animate in on scroll
- [ ] Calorie ring animates to target percentage
- [ ] Sidebar collapses/expands smoothly
- [ ] Theme toggle switches colors with smooth transition
- [ ] All 4 routes navigable via sidebar
- [ ] Mobile layout: no sidebar, bottom nav visible, cards stack vertically
- [ ] Hover effects work on all cards and buttons
