## Known Pitfalls

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| Framer Motion `ease` array type error | Use `as const`: `ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] as const` |
| Framer Motion `type` string type error | Use `as const`: `type: 'spring' as const` |
| `useTheme` crashes during SSR prerender | Give `ThemeContext` a default value, never `undefined` |
| `border-radius` flickers with Framer Motion 3D transforms | Put `overflow: hidden` + `border-radius` on a parent div, animate the child |
| Recharts SSR hydration mismatch | Wrap charts in a client component with `'use client'` directive |
| Recharts `ResponsiveContainer` renders 0 height | Always set explicit `height` prop or wrapper min-height |
| Next.js 16 `metadata` export type | Import `Metadata` from `next` — don't use old `Head` component |
| Tailwind v4 config | No `tailwind.config.ts` needed — use CSS `@theme` blocks |
